txt.en: 'You believe you have the awareness of Caras Galadhon and the quickness to be named a flet-runner? I and my friends will be the judge of that. Can you complete my challenge?\n\n'Reach the flet-runner by the Caras Galadhon Stable-master with utmost haste, and we will see!'
'Very good, [placeholder]. You have impressed me with your quickness and knowledge of the city.'
'Time is wasting, [placeholder]! You are seeking the flet-runner by the Caras Galadhon Stable-master!'
Leginiel has challenged you to prove your familiarity with Caras Galadhon in a race through the trees.
